{"tid":858878,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《YG戰資》扮清朝人自稱是豬被轟辱華 社長道歉被斥無誠意","createTime":"2018-10-12T06:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T08:58:01.000Z","uid":75969,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3eb67ea9f91ffc7152f53a6f3b2f63d532bf011a","tid":858878,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T06:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181011/_2018101119180077314.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181011%2F_2018101119180077314.jpg&h=ceaf8635&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">《YG戰略資料本部》節目被批辱華。網圖</span><br />\n<br />\n韓國3大經紀與娛樂公司YG事務所，近日與影片串流平台Netflix合作拍攝網絡節目《YG戰略資料本部》。節目中所用的中國地圖不完整，加上有藝人扮清朝人以中文說「我是豬」，令不少内地網民認為節目辱華。YG事務所負責人梁鉉錫今日下午於社交媒體上道歉，内地網民紛紛留言批評，指「看不出一點誠意」。<br />\n<br />\n節目於10月5日播出，網民發現節目中所使用的中國地圖不完整，欠缺東南沿海地區省分，加上台灣位置正好被藝人的手擋住，網民認為節目該舉動破壞中國領土完整。另外，節目中2名韓國藝人扮成清朝人，並在被警方逮捕後，以中文說「我是豬」。事件引起網民反感，紛紛到負責人梁鉉錫Instagram賬號中留言批評，並要求梁鉉錫公開道歉。<br />\n<br />\n梁鉉錫今日下午在Instagram上發文，以中文及韓文致歉，文中指「向中國的各位粉絲鄭重地道歉。已經向相關負責人下達指令，盡快修改和刪除錯誤內容。今後將更加注意和小心。」<br />\n<br />\n不過，内地網民明顯不接受梁鉉錫的道歉，網民留言「給粉絲道歉？不是應該給中國道歉嗎？」、「就這樣敷衍了事？」、「中國人和中國地圖不是能被你這種人侮辱的」、「不接受」、「看不出一點誠意」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181011/_2018101119180130551.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181011%2F_2018101119180130551.jpg&h=21165e63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">YG事務所負責人梁鉉錫在Instagram上道歉。梁鉉錫IG截圖</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/838708\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F838708&d=WS%2FYp3ECWde12OldG2sREYsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=96c6b7db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F838708&h=aeb61f7a\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/838708</a>"},{"pid":"3a65cfc3fc7679b2248f33ee54c12f14075828e2","tid":858878,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T06:13:19.000Z","msg":"對住支那人講事實係唔可以太大聲<br />\nD生蕃唔係人咁品"},{"pid":"e67ec4b18a333b5a384a89786773b310d6d5b2cf","tid":858878,"uid":46245,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T06:19:26.000Z","msg":"老實講，我覺得將辱清朝人等同辱華人呢一點係更大侮辱囉，當然而家所謂「中國人」覺得將漢人滅族奴化既元朝清朝都視為中國人仲要視之為光榮根本唔知咩係侮辱"},{"pid":"b2b4c6f0e24a0694c6eaf23e84f6cae7f6772151","tid":858878,"uid":91633,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T06:29:22.000Z","msg":"清朝根本就係衣家個支共咁<br />\n其他表面友好<br />\n實際由心睇你唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由明朝滅亡個刻日本韓國已經將中國睇成蠻夷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1853993b82b0f1e7a099afd1c774fab67f0ca1ab","tid":858878,"uid":61363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T08:31:08.000Z","msg":"清朝人係外族人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾著我係大陸網民一定拍手叫好"},{"pid":"bde6961e3e039e509c9c54f88e0c4cb7292cbf55","tid":858878,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T08:36:29.000Z","msg":"大陸睇到Netflix咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45d0f69ea7006b790f23c6cd2c40d666e461f3b","tid":858878,"uid":69090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T08:51:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11d1b7cf83a98014f82c2f6fb28cdaee2f5e206b","tid":858878,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T08:56:26.000Z","msg":"滿清唔係外族侵略咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9182e8cd4382b66265f55030adbba0aff16ee6f3","tid":858878,